00:00 Sophie Turner Stars as Lara Croft in the Tomb Raider Live-Action Series
The "Tomb Raider" live-action series finally has a lead actress. According to Deadline, "Game of Thrones" star Sophie Turner will indeed take on the role of Lara Croft. She had been among the top contenders for the iconic role for quite some time.

1:45 Call of Duty Is Being Made Into a Movie!
With over 500 million copies sold, "Call of Duty" is still one of the most successful video game series of all time. Reason enough for a film adaptation, which according to industry magazine The Hollywood Reporter is currently in the works at Paramount Pictures.
